Detailed Description

Iterator through real Boxes (not periodic images) in a const BoxContainer.

RealBoxConstIterator is an iterator that provides methods for stepping through a BoxContainer, skipping periodic images.

Example usage: 

 *  BoxContainer mapped_boxes;
 *  // fill in mapped_boxes
 *  for ( RealBoxConstIterator ni(mapped_boxes); ni.isValid(); ++ni ) {
 *    TBOX_ASSERT( ! ni->isPeriodicImage() );
 *  }
 *
